& [SLMSlice53LexiconLicenseProvenanceAudit] is a work-ready SOP slice for lexical authority provenance
  + [slice_id] is SLM-53
  + [status] is specification_complete
  + [effort] is S-M
  + [risk] is low
  + [depends_on] is SLM-13, SLM-52
  + [scope] is audit source provenance, license notes, retrieval hashes, and generated artifact boundaries
  + [acceptance_criteria] is lexical substrate authority can cite every imported source
  + [proof_route] is SOP review and source provenance file inspection

  ! [CompletionEvidence] is the SLM-53 SOP verification record
    @ [contract] is slm_project/specifications/contracts/SLM_Lexicon_License_Provenance_Audit.sop
    @ [source_manifest] inspected
    @ [source_provenance] inspected
    @ [substrate_manifest] inspected
